        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a separate, dry pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>pistachio nuts </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once done, transfer to a chopping board and set aside to cool (save the pan for later!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1652874074182-x200.jpg",
