            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>bulgur</strong> <strong>wheat</strong> with 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan with the pepper and mix everything together</p><p>Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until almost all of the water is absorbed</p><p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat, keep covered, and set aside</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1652874083264-x200.jpg",
