            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the bulgur is cooking, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Crumble your <strong>feta</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop the <strong>cooled pistachios</strong> coarsely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1652874084494-x200.jpg",
