        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-low heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, crack your <strong>egg[s] </strong>into the pan</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p><p>Remove the <strong>fried egg[s]</strong> from the heat and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
