            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the bulgur and add the<strong> chopped herbs</strong>,<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped pistachios </strong>and<strong> half</strong> the <strong>crumbled</strong> <strong>feta</strong> (save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>jewelled bulgur with feta</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
