      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top the <strong>jewelled bulgur with feta</strong> with a <strong>fried</strong> <strong>egg </strong>and<strong> </strong>sprinkle over your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>sumac</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped</strong> <strong>pistachios</strong> and <strong>remaining crumbled feta</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
